data.description: Nestled on an expansive hilltop lot, this home boasts breathtaking panoramic views and an impeccably designed interior! As you step inside, the grandeur of the living room captures your attention with its high ceilings and abundant natural light, creating an inviting ambiance for relaxation and entertaining. The well-appointed kitchen features sleek granite countertops, a center island, and a breakfast bar. The primary suite is impressively spacious! It features a layout that includes a sitting area, and is complete with a spa-like ensuite bathroom. Additionally, your 3-car garage provides both convenience and added storage capacity. Beyond the elegant interiors, the outdoor space is perfect for gatherings or simply relaxing while taking in the spectacular views from your hilltop retreat. Don’t wait– Schedule your private tour today!
